platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 展開太空間諜戰，到底誰是內鬼？
みんなで挑む、宇宙船の危機
扮演船員或殺手 展開太空間諜戰

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Everyone’s suspicious in Among Us!, a fascinating multiplayer game set aboard a damaged spaceship. Whether you’re a Crewmate making quick repairs or an Impostor taking out key systems (and unsuspecting players), each match is a riveting mystery. And a hilarious one, especially when smart accusations or sly misdirection sway who gets voted off the ship. It’s a test of wits anyone can enjoy.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Customize your look with Halloween-themed hats.
